column5: Has anyone fished Scugog lately? I'm going on Fri aft and staying out there till Sun. Renting a hut in Cesearea. Any reports. Thanks.

i was there last friday...north end of the lake...went in the morning, and didn't get fishing till about 8am. so i missed the morning bite. ended up with a bunch of small perch. i'm hoping to go back up for the night bite this weekend.
My son has a hut off Goreskys Marina on the west side of the Island. Hes getting some pickeral but only small ones.
I was out Tues. out of Ceserea. Landed four.  Sweedish pimples with a minnow just off  off bottom jigging. Watch on the drop, The weather on the weekand should be better.  Good Luck.
